# Trivy ignore file — CVEs in upstream pre-built binaries that cannot be
# remediated by bumping tool versions because upstream projects have not yet
# released builds compiled with Go 1.25.7 / Go 1.24.13+.
#
# Affected binaries (agent image): helm, kubectl, kubeconform, kustomize,
# stern, flux, talosctl, sops, yq.
#
# These are NOT suppressions for code we own. The mendabot-watcher and
# mendabot-agent (age/age-keygen) binaries are compiled with Go 1.25.7 and
# are clean.
#
# Expiry: 2026-06-01 — re-evaluate at that date. If upstream tools still
# have not released Go 1.25.7 builds, extend the expiry and document why.

# CRITICAL — crypto/tls session resumption (needs Go 1.24.13 or 1.25.7)
